last_episode_to_air.name: One Band of Robbers
last_episode_to_air.overview: Mattis and Borka come head-to-head as Cappa makes her final attempt at revenge. A new phase of life begins, and Ronja must say a difficult goodbye.

name: Ronja the Robber's Daughter
overview: Loving, loyal and unafraid, the daughter of a wanted robber chief makes a secret friend in her father's magical and treacherous forest.

episodes.name: One Eye to the Sky
episodes.overview: Young Ronja learns to protect herself from the dangers of the Mattis Woods while Borka and his robbers cause Mattis trouble.

episodes.name: The Robber Chief
episodes.overview: At Hell's Mouth, Ronja unearths a disturbing secret about the Borka robbers. In the village, Halvert is under pressure to make the forest safe.

episodes.name: The Pillory
episodes.overview: Ronja learns something shocking about the robbers' way of life, while Mattis recruits a new member for the clan. Birk and Ronja meet again.

episodes.name: The First Snow
episodes.overview: Ronja and Birk secretly spend their autumn days together in the forest, while Mattis creates obstacles for Borka. Cappa has a new plan.

episodes.name: My Brother
episodes.overview: Winter separates Ronja and Birk, who must remain inside the Mattis Fortress and the Borka Keep. Ronja learns why her father hates Borka.

episodes.name: The Spring Shout
episodes.overview: It's spring and Ronja and Birk can finally reunite in the Mattis Woods. Mattis suspects that a robber stole food from the pantry during winter.

episodes.name: I Have No Child
episodes.overview: Cappa and her knights are after Ronja and Chegge while Mattis enacts a shocking plan to get rid of Borka once and for all.

episodes.name: Into the Wild
episodes.overview: Everything has changed in the Mattis Fortress. Ronja and Birk weigh their options as their fathers' strife deepens.

episodes.name: Bear Cavern
episodes.overview: Both the knights and the wile-wings are after Ronja and Birk, who must find a new refuge. Their friendship is put to a test.

episodes.name: Mattis
episodes.overview: The Mattis robbers struggle to get their chief back on his feet, and ask Ronja to return home. Cappa makes a new plan to capture Mattis.

episodes.name: Coming Home
episodes.overview: Lovis has had enough of Mattis' antics. Ronja receives a surprise guest and Birk worries about the future, while Cappa reveals what is haunting her.

episodes.name: One Band of Robbers
episodes.overview: Mattis and Borka come head-to-head as Cappa makes her final attempt at revenge. A new phase of life begins, and Ronja must say a difficult goodbye.
